<main>
  <section style="padding: 4rem 0; background: #f8f9fa;">
    <div class="container"><h1>Disclaimer</h1><p style="color: #666;">Last updated: June 16, 2026</p></div>
  </section>
  <section style="padding: 3rem 0;">
    <div class="container" style="max-width: 800px; line-height: 1.9;">
      <h2>Independent Platform</h2>
      <p>PakistanBill.online is an independent utility bill information platform. We are <strong>not affiliated with, endorsed by, or connected to</strong> any of the following organizations: WAPDA, PEPCO, PITC, LESCO, MEPCO, GEPCO, FESCO, IESCO, PESCO, HESCO, SEPCO, QESCO, TESCO, AJKED, K-Electric, SNGPL, SSGC, PTCL, WASA Lahore, WASA Rawalpindi, WASA Faisalabad, NEPRA, OGRA, or the Government of Pakistan.</p>

      <h2>Bill Data Accuracy</h2>
      <p>Bill data displayed through our tool is fetched directly and in real-time from official government portals. We do not modify, store, or alter any bill data. However, we cannot guarantee the accuracy, completeness, or timeliness of data returned by third-party government systems. For any billing disputes, always refer to the original bill issued by your utility provider.</p>

      <h2>Tariff Information</h2>
      <p>Tariff rates, surcharge details, and fee information on this website are provided for informational purposes based on publicly available NEPRA and OGRA notifications. Rates may change following NEPRA hearings, government relief packages, or quarterly adjustments. Always verify the exact rates applied to your account from your official monthly bill.</p>

      <h2>No Official Relationship</h2>
      <p>Using PakistanBill.online does not create any relationship between you and any utility company. All billing disputes, connection issues, payment arrangements, and complaints must be directed to your utility provider directly. We provide helpline numbers, official website links, and contact information for all providers on their respective pages.</p>

      <h2>Limitation of Liability</h2>
      <p>PakistanBill.online shall not be held liable for any losses, damages, or inconveniences arising from reliance on information provided on this website. Use all information in conjunction with official communications from your utility provider.</p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>For questions about this disclaimer, email <a href="mailto:info@pakistanbill.online">info@pakistanbill.online</a> or visit our <a href="/contact/">Contact page</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>
<footer class="site-footer">
